<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>쇼츠 홍보관 - RANKING AI</title>
    <style>
        body { background: #0b0c0d; color: #fff; font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding-bottom: 100px; }
        a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; height: 8px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #0b0c0d; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #333; border-radius: 4px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #ff5722; }
        .main-header { background: #121314; border-bottom: 1px solid #222; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
        .header-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 15px 40px; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1b1c; }
        .logo { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1px; background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff5722, #ffb300); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .top-search-form { display: flex; align-items: center; background: #222; border: 2px solid #ff5722; border-radius: 25px; padding: 5px 15px; width: 400px; }
        .top-search-input { background: none; border: none; color: white; outline: none; flex: 1; font-size: 15px; padding: 5px; }
        .top-search-btn { background: none; border: none; color: #ff5722; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; padding: 0 10px; }
        .auth-buttons { display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center; }
        .btn-login { color: #bbb; font-size: 14px; }
        .btn-signup { background: #ff5722; color: #000; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; }
        .header-nav { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 40px; padding: 12px 0; background: #0b0c0d; }
        .nav-item { color: #aaa; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; transition: 0.2s; position: relative; }
        .nav-item:hover, .nav-item.active { color: #ff5722; }
        .nav-item.active::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -12px; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 3px; background: #ff5722; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="main-header">
       <div class="header-top">
            <div class="logo">RANKING AI</div>
            <form action="/" method="GET" class="top-search-form">
                <input type="text" name="search" class="top-search-input" placeholder="아티스트 검색...">
                <button type="submit" class="top-search-btn">🔍</button>
            </form>
            <div class="auth-buttons">
                <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>
                    <span style="color: #aaa; font-size: 14px;"><%= user.id %>님</span>
                    <a href="/logout" class="btn-login">로그아웃</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/login" class="btn-login">로그인</a>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn-signup">회원가입</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="header-nav">
            <a href="/?sort=views" class="nav-item">RANKING AI 챠트</a>
            <a href="/?sort=latest" class="nav-item">최신음악</a>
            <a href="/?genre=K-POP" class="nav-item">장르별</a>
            <a href="/youtube" class="nav-item">유튜브</a>
            <a href="/shorts" class="nav-item active">쇼츠</a>
            <a href="/board" class="nav-item">커뮤니티</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <style>
            .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
            .page-header { border-bottom: 2px solid #222; padding-bottom: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px; }
            .page-title { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0; color: #fff; }
            .add-video-form { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex: 1; max-width: 500px; }
            .add-video-input { flex: 1; background: #222; border: 1px solid #444; color: #fff; padding: 10px 15px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; outline: none; }
            .add-video-input:focus { border-color: #ff5722; }
            .btn-submit { background: #ff5722; color: #000; border: none; padding: 0 20px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; }
            .video-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
            .video-card-wrap { position: relative; }
            .video-card { background: #161718; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #222; transition: all 0.3s ease; display: block; position: relative; cursor: pointer; }
            .video-card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.2); border-color: #ff5722; }
            .thumb-wrapper { position: relative; width: 100%; padding-top: 177.77%; background: #000; overflow: hidden; }
            .thumb-img { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; transition: transform 0.4s ease; }
            .video-card:hover .thumb-img { transform: scale(1.08); opacity: 0.6; }
            .play-icon { position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); font-size: 50px; color: #ff5722; opacity: 0; transition: 0.3s; z-index: 10; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.8)); }
            .video-card:hover .play-icon { opacity: 1; }
            .shorts-badge { position: absolute; top: 10px; left: 10px; background: red; color: white; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; z-index: 5; }
            .video-info { padding: 15px; }
            .video-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #fff; line-height: 1.4; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden; }
            .video-meta { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 12px; color: #aaa; }
            .video-author { color: #ff5722; background: rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.1); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: bold; }

            /* 🌟 쇼츠는 세로형 팝업창! */
            .modal-overlay { display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85); z-index: 9999; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }
            .modal-content { position: relative; height: 85vh; aspect-ratio: 9/16; background: #000; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
            .modal-content iframe { width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; border-radius: 12px; }
            .close-btn { position: absolute; top: -45px; right: 0; color: #fff; font-size: 40px; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s; }
            .close-btn:hover { color: #ff5722; }

            @media (max-width: 900px) {
                .page-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
                .add-video-form { width: 100%; max-width: 100%; flex-direction: column; }
                .video-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 10px; }
                .modal-content { width: 90%; height: auto; } /* 모바일 모달 비율 보정 */
            }
        </style>

        <div class="page-header">
            <h2 class="page-title">📱 쇼츠(Shorts) 홍보관</h2>
            <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>
                <form action="/add-shorts" method="POST" class="add-video-form">
                    <input type="text" name="title" class="add-video-input" placeholder="쇼츠 제목" required style="flex: 0.5;">
                    <input type="text" name="youtubeLink" class="add-video-input" placeholder="쇼츠 링크 (예: https://youtube.com/shorts/...)" required>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">+ 등록</button>
                </form>
            <% } else { %>
                <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #777;">쇼츠 등록은 <a href="/login" style="color:#ff5722;">로그인</a> 후 가능합니다.</div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="video-grid">
            <% if (typeof shorts !== 'undefined' && shorts.length > 0) { %>
                <% shorts.forEach(video => { %>
                    <div class="video-card-wrap">
                        <a href="<%= video.url %>" class="video-card" onclick="event.preventDefault(); const url = '<%= video.url %>'; const id = url.split('v=')[1]?.substring(0,11) || url.split('youtu.be/')[1]?.substring(0,11) || url.split('shorts/')[1]?.substring(0,11); if(id){ document.getElementById('shIframe').src = 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/'+id+'?autoplay=1'; document.getElementById('shModal').style.display='flex'; } else { window.open(url); }">
                            <div class="shorts-badge">Shorts</div>
                            <div class="thumb-wrapper">
                                <img src="<%= video.thumbnail %>" class="thumb-img" alt="썸네일">
                                <div class="play-icon">▶</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="video-info">
                                <h3 class="video-title"><%= video.title %></h3>
                                <div class="video-meta">
                                    <span class="video-author">@<%= video.uploader %></span>
                                    <span><%= new Date(video.createdAt).toLocaleDateString() %></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                        
                        <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user && (user.role === 'admin' || user.id === video.uploader)) { %>
                            <form action="/delete-video/<%= video._id %>" method="POST" style="position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px; z-index: 20;" onsubmit="return confirm('정말 삭제하시겠습니까?');">
                                <button type="submit" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8); color: #ff4a4a; border: 1px solid #ff4a4a; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold;">🗑️ 삭제</button>
                            </form>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
                <div style="grid-column: 1 / -1; text-align: center; padding: 100px 0; background: #161718; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px dashed #333; color: #555;">
                    <div style="font-size: 50px; margin-bottom: 15px;">📱</div>
                    아직 등록된 쇼츠(Shorts) 영상이 없습니다.
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div id="shModal" class="modal-overlay" onclick="if(event.target === this) { document.getElementById('shIframe').src=''; this.style.display='none'; }">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="document.getElementById('shIframe').src=''; document.getElementById('shModal').style.display='none';">&times;</span>
                <iframe id="shIframe" src="" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
